  <mainContent><![CDATA[<h2>Course Overview</h2>
<p>A-Level Classical Civilisation enables you to explore the roots of the modern world through studying the history, literature and art of ancient Greece and Rome. As part of this course you will visit the British Museum and take in theatre performances of Greek Tragedy and/or Comedy in your first year. There is also the chance to visit Rome or Athens in the second year.</p>]]></mainContent>
